{"tid":608292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧詩晚裝成焦點　冧莊傑出運動員","createTime":"2018-03-28T04:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T14:42:19.000Z","uid":2644,"like":17,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"fba9c3ffab495d915e9952ff86bf828dbf6a0ac2","tid":608292,"uid":2644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李慧詩冧莊　晚裝成焦點<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/03/28/1802828_8f879239fa749660f4b49d7f06d33d3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2F1802828_8f879239fa749660f4b49d7f06d33d3a.jpg&h=05f04f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「體壇奧斯卡」之稱的「2017年度香港傑出運動員選舉」，昨晚在灣仔會展舉行頒獎禮，在賽道上屢傷屢戰、外形硬朗的「牛下女車神」李慧詩【圖】，由大家常見的戰衣，換上略帶性感晚禮服，成焦點之一。至於8名當選「傑出運動員」健兒，除李慧詩外，有桌球的吳安儀、游泳何詩蓓、乒乓球黃鎮廷、劍擊張家朗、武術何健欣、輪椅劍擊余翠怡，及乒乓球吳玫薈（香港智障人士體育協會）；其中吳安儀更力壓李慧詩，重奪失落一屆的「星中之星」最高榮譽大獎。"},{"pid":"e01346e8dd87d430ae9494e22b7b4c11a74e1658","tid":608292,"uid":123335,"like":104,"dislike":20,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"好似 141"},{"pid":"558bf5007a7b46d527e185b44927dd10bfecd218","tid":608292,"uid":55851,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"老咗30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb31dd667f63b04c891e4a8387ed985defe0b8","tid":608292,"uid":102096,"like":14,"dislike":83,"score":-69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0fac395fefe10a84e72450bac25d75b520b526e","tid":608292,"uid":21028,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"quote":{"pid":"dbbb31dd667f63b04c891e4a8387ed985defe0b8","tid":608292,"uid":102096,"like":14,"dislike":83,"score":-69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"巴打食開呢類??"},{"pid":"81cc5142afbff5ffb071e4a22d9ca5f4cac82d08","tid":608292,"u